WEBVTT

00:03:28.077 --> 00:03:30.417
Yaxshi xabar ham yo'q emas.

00:03:30.417 --> 00:03:34.817
Kortizolning stress holatidagi miyangizga 
ta’sirini susaytirishning yo'llari mavjud.

00:03:34.817 --> 00:03:38.713
Jismoniy mashq va chuqur nafas olish, 
atrofingizga

00:03:38.713 --> 00:03:40.376
diqqat qaratish va e’tiborli

00:03:40.376 --> 00:03:43.521
bo’lishga chorlovchi meditatsiya 
eng samarali vositalardir.

00:03:43.521 --> 00:03:46.255
Har ikkala mashg’ulot stress ta'sirini
kamaytirib,

00:03:46.255 --> 00:03:49.525
gippokamp hajmini kattalashtiradi

00:03:49.525 --> 00:03:51.770
va shu yo’l bilan xotirangizni 
yaxshilaydi.

00:03:51.770 --> 00:03:54.470
Kundalik turmush mashaqqatlaridan 
bukilmang.

00:03:54.470 --> 00:03:59.228
Stress sizni o’z yo’rig’iga 
solishdan avval, siz uni jilovlang.